\item Temperature rows already in \code{df} (measured on grab-sample days) are
interpolated along with other analytes.
\item An external daily temperature series supplied via the \code{temperature}
argument (e.g. from \code{\link[=estimate_water_temp]{estimate_water_temp()}}) fills in days without a
grab temperature.  Grab-sample-day measurements take priority.
}
Set \code{require_temperature = FALSE} only for datasets that do not contain
